        <ul>
          <li>All AI-generated content, reports, recommendations, and outputs are <strong>advisory only</strong> and not guaranteed to be accurate, complete, or up-to-date</li>
          <li>AI systems may produce errors, hallucinations, or biased outputs</li>
          <li>AI-generated content should always be verified by qualified human professionals</li>
          <li>We do not guarantee that AI outputs will meet your specific needs or expectations</li>
          <li>The quality of AI outputs depends on the quality and completeness of input data provided by you</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>2. No Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>The information, reports, recommendations, and content provided through our Services <strong>do not constitute professional advice</strong>:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Legal:</strong> Our Services do not provide legal advice. Consult a licensed attorney for legal matters.</li>
