          <li><strong>Security:</strong> Website audits and security scans identify potential issues but do not guarantee that all vulnerabilities will be found or that your systems are fully secure.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>3. Website Audit Results</h2>
        <p>Our website audit, SEO analysis, performance testing, and security scanning tools:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide <strong>recommendations only</strong> — not guarantees of improvement</li>
          <li>Are based on automated analysis and may not identify all issues</li>
          <li>May produce false positives or miss certain problems</li>
          <li>Should be reviewed by qualified web developers or security professionals</li>
          <li>Results may vary based on website changes, third-party integrations, and evolving standards</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>4. HIPAA Compliance Tools</h2>
        <p>For healthcare clients using our HIPAA compliance scanners and tools:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Our tools are <strong>aids to help identify potential compliance gaps</strong>, not guarantees of HIPAA compliance</li>
          <li>Achieving and maintaining HIPAA compliance requires ongoing effort, training, and professional oversight</li>
          <li>Passing our scanner does not guarantee compliance with HIPAA regulations</li>
          <li>You are solely responsible for ensuring your organization meets all applicable healthcare regulations</li>
          <li>Consult a qualified HIPAA compliance professional for comprehensive compliance assessment</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>5. Results May Vary</h2>
        <p>Individual results from using our Services will vary based on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>The nature and condition of your existing systems and website</li>
          <li>Your implementation of recommendations</li>
          <li>External factors beyond our control (search engine algorithm changes, third-party service changes, etc.)</li>
          <li>The accuracy and completeness of information you provide</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We make no guarantees about specific outcomes, improvements, or returns from using our Services.</p>
        <h2>6. Third-Party Integrations</h2>
        <p>Our Services may integrate with or reference third-party tools, platforms, and services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>We do not control and are not responsible for third-party services</li>
          <li>Third-party integrations may change, break, or become unavailable without notice</li>
          <li>We do not guarantee compatibility with all third-party systems</li>
          <li>Third-party terms of service and privacy policies apply to your use of those services</li>
          <li>We are not liable for issues arising from third-party services</li>
        </ul>
